title: Thinking about leaving Florida tomorrow tonight.
body:
Have 1 case of water in my trunk, couple cans food, kitchen knives and my M&P shield in my glove compartment.
All packed and ready to go when shit hit the fan, I'm taking my toys with me because people out here are crazy.
